<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.futilitycloset.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/2025-10-15-black-and-white.png" alt="clausén chess problem" width="381" height="387" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-71940" srcset="https://www.futilitycloset.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/2025-10-15-black-and-white.png 381w, https://www.futilitycloset.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/2025-10-15-black-and-white-300x305.png 300w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 381px) 100vw, 381px" /></p>
<p>By Sigurd Clausén. White to mate in three moves.</p>

